#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:1
msgid "E0027"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `deprecated_syntax`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:5
msgid ""
"The syntax is deprecated. Please refer to the warning message on the "
"reason and potential fix."
msgstr "语法已弃用。请参考警告消息，了解原因和潜在修复方法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:7
msgid ""
"For example, one of the deprecated usage is using constructors as "
"functions. Instead, partial application should be used to create a "
"function from a constructor."
msgstr "例如，其中一种已废弃的用法是将构造函数用作函数。相反，应使用部分应用来从构造函数创建一个函数。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:12
msgid ""
"enum Message {\n"
"  Add(String)\n"
"} derive(Show)\n"
"\n"
"fn perform[T](message : (T) -> Message, produce : () -> T) -> Message {\n"
"  //\n"
"  // Warning: The syntax fn f[..] for declaring polymorphic function is \n"
"  // deprecated. Use fn[..] f instead.\n"
"  message(produce())\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  println(perform(Add, fn() { \"Hello, world!\" }))\n"
"  //              ^^^\n"
"  // Warning: Using constructor as function directly is\n"
"  // deprecated. Use the partial application syntax instead\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:18
msgid ""
"Migrate the code according to the warning message. In this case, the code"
" should be changed to use the partial application syntax."
msgstr "根据警告信息迁移代码。在这种情况下，应将代码修改为使用部分应用语法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:21
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"enum Message {\n"
"  Add(String)\n"
"} derive(Show)\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn[T] perform(message : (T) -> Message, produce : () -> T) -> Message {\n"
"  message(produce())\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  println(perform(Add(_), fn() { \"Hello, world!\" }))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

